data.eml:eml: The sea lice (Copepoda: Caligidae) of Moreton Bay (Queensland, Australia), with descriptions of thirteen new species

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Boxshall, Geoff (2018): The sea lice (Copepoda: Caligidae) of Moreton Bay (Queensland, Australia), with descriptions of thirteen new species. Zootaxa 4398 (1): 1-172, DOI: https://doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.4398.1.1
